    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sites known by archaeological evidence of hominind activity, but not known to be a settled community. Distinguished from "inhabited places," which are known to be communities.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
